comment: Jordan (LAC) makes marginal contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Carter (MEM) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Gasol (MEM) sets the screen on Paul (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jordan (LAC) makes contact with the ball with his hand and does not intentionally kick it.
Paul (LAC) makes marginal contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his SQBR.
Conley (MEM) dislodges Paul (LAC), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Gasol (MEM) legally contests Paul's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Ennis (MEM) sets the screen on Mbah a Moute (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Griffin (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on the shot attempt by Randolph (MEM).
Gasol (MEM) and Jordan (LAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of MEM ball is upheld.
Mbah a Moute (LAC) makes marginal contact with Carter (MEM) that does not affect his FOM.
Paul (LAC) makes contact with Ennis' (MEM) right wrist and affects his driving shot attempt.
Conley (MEM) makes incidental contact with Crawford (LAC) that does not affect his FOM.
Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
Ennis (MEM) makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
